OL,4,Cdecade-old murder case
OL,6,FPolice were called to the scene near
OL,7,FPentre-llyn-Cymmer and Llyn Brenig and
OL,8,Ffound fully decomposed remains of a
OL,9,Fman, believed to have been buried in a
OL,10,Fshallow grave between 1995 and 2005.
OL,12,FClothes discovered near the remains
OL,13,Fincluded a dark green Pringle jumper,
OL,14,Fand dark red decomposed Marks &
OL,15,FSpencer underwear.
OL,17,FNorth Wales Police has now said the
OL,18,Finvestigation is being reviewed by its
OL,19,Fmajor crime review team in a bid to
OL,20,Fidentify the man and the circumstances
OL,21,Faround his death.
