OL,6,FTests at the time showed he had
OL,7,Fsuffered head trauma.
OL,9,FA police spokesperson in November 2025
OL,10,Fsaid: "We can confirm an investigation
OL,11,Finto a body found in Clocaenog Forest
OL,12,Fin November 2015 is being reviewed by
OL,13,FNorth Wales Police's recently formed
OL,14,FMajor Crime Review Team.
OL,16,F"The team of detectives are working
OL,17,Fwith the National Crime Agency and a
OL,18,Fleading team of specialists across the
OL,19,Fcountry to help identify the man."
